title: Ep. 48 - Gender-Confused Boys Beat A Bunch Of Girls In A Girl's Track Meet
description:
Yet again, gender-confused boys were allowed to compete against girls in a track and field meet, and they of course blew out the competition. This madness needs to end. Parents need to step up. Pull your daughters out of these competitions so long as boys are allowed to participate.
